Package com.alicecallsbob.fcsdk.android.phone

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AudioDeviceManager
    Manages the audio device options presented by the hardware.
    AudioDeviceManagerListener
    A listener for the AudioDeviceManager to indicate when the list of audio devices has changed.
    Call
    An object that represents a voice and/or video call.
    CallListener
    A listener for the Call that will be informed of events.
    Phone
    An object that acts as the entry point for all voice and video calls.
    PhoneListener
    A listener for the Phone that will be informed of events.
    PhoneVideoCaptureSetting
    Interface for video capture settings.
    VideoSurfaceListener  
  • Class Summary

    Builder pattern factory for CallStatusInfo objects
    VideoSurface
    A SurfaceView that renders frames from local & remote VideoTracks.
